  <T n="tooltip">0xE2B9076C<!--String: "\n<b><font color='#2182E6'>When it is Hot or Cold go outside in unsuitable clothing or stand near objects that will make {0.SimFirstName} hotter or colder. Have {0.SimPronounObjective} become dangerously hot or cold. (But don't die!)</font></b>\n\nDid you know some Sims freeze into icicles or burst into flames!? Well, that's not going to be me! I'm going to risk it, and get either super hot or super cold, and I'm going to withstand it! They'll call me Danger Kid!"--></T>
